        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Getting started]]></title>
            <link>https://vitepress-blog-theme.vercel.app/content/posts/Hello.html</link>
            <guid>https://vitepress-blog-theme.vercel.app/content/posts/Hello.html</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Mar 2023 14:27:31 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="_1-安装主题" tabindex="-1">1. 安装主题 <a class="header-anchor" href="#_1-安装主题" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;1. 安装主题&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<p>在 <a href="https://github.com/fzdwx/vitepress-blog-theme/releases" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">https://github.com/fzdwx/vitepress-blog-theme/releases</a> 页面下载操作系统对应的 bang 压缩文件.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>bang 是 vitepress-blog-theme 的命令行工具, 用于快速创建博客, 更新主题等</p>
</blockquote>
<p>然后运行 <code>bang init</code></p>
<p>就会在当前目录下生成一个 <code>vitepress-blog-theme</code> 的文件夹, 这个其实也是通过 <code>git clone</code> 实现的, 只是删除了一些不必要的文件</p>
<div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre v-pre class="shiki material-theme-palenight" ><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #676E95; font-style: italic"># 运行项目</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #82AAFF">cd</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #C3E88D">vitepress-blog-theme</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #FFCB6B">pnpm</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #C3E88D">i</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #FFCB6B">pnpm</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #C3E88D">dev</span></span></code></pre>
</div><p>接下来可以运行 <code>bang new</code> 来创建一篇文章,</p>
<div class="language-shell"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">shell</span><pre v-pre class="shiki material-theme-palenight" ><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #FFCB6B">bang</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #C3E88D">new</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #676E95; font-style: italic"># 交互式创建文章</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #FFCB6B">bang</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #C3E88D">new</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #C3E88D">-t</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span><span style="color: #C3E88D">文章标题</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #676E95; font-style: italic"># 直接创建文章</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #FFCB6B">bang</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #C3E88D">-t</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span><span style="color: #C3E88D">标题</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #C3E88D">-l</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span><span style="color: #C3E88D">post</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #C3E88D">-g</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span><span style="color: #C3E88D">group</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #C3E88D">new</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #676E95; font-style: italic"># -l 支持 post, doc, -g 只在 doc 下使用</span></span></code></pre>
</div><p>所有的文章都在 <code>content/</code> 文件夹下</p>
<p>如果后续需要更新主题, 可以使用 <code>bang update</code> 命令</p>
<h2 id="_2-部署" tabindex="-1">2. 部署 <a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-部署" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;2. 部署&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<p>可以通过 <code>Github action</code> 自动部署到 <code>Github Pages</code> 上, 也可以使用 <code>Vercel</code>.</p>
<h3 id="_2-1-github-action" tabindex="-1">2.1 Github action <a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-1-github-action" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;2.1 Github action&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h3>
<p>如果使用 <code>Github action</code> 部署, 仅需将 <code>deploy.yml.example</code> 重命名为 <code>deploy.yml</code> 即可</p>
<p><img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65269574/227693247-cd247b3c-bf2d-4ceb-8f8a-9df58c8a4150.png" alt="image"></p>
<h3 id="_2-2-vercel" tabindex="-1">2.2 Vercel <a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-2-vercel" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;2.2 Vercel&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h3>
<p>需要修改构建命令为:</p>
<p><img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65269574/227693554-f851cf22-dd51-48db-9fd5-d81446227862.png" alt="image"></p>
<p>更多配置请参考 <a href="https://vitepress.dev/guide/deploy#netlify-vercel-cloudflare-pages-aws-amplify-render" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">https://vitepress.dev/guide/deploy#netlify-vercel-cloudflare-pages-aws-amplify-render</a></p>
<h2 id="_3-note" tabindex="-1">3. Note <a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-note" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;3. Note&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<ol>
<li>设置 Github token 到 <code>Github action</code> 中
<img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65269574/227569403-ac21c7fa-ed22-45e2-824d-1fa293ce0ac7.png" alt="image"></li>
<li>修改 <code>repo</code> 为你当前仓库的名称
<img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65269574/227692648-79b74a2e-b597-40a3-a7c0-6acc85a75d5a.png" alt="image"></li>
<li>Github action 需要开启读写权限 <code>Read and write permissions</code>
<img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/65269574/227569746-8e615cca-69f4-488c-a1a9-5849eb40327f.png" alt="image"></li>
</ol>
]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Layout]]></title>
            <link>https://vitepress-blog-theme.vercel.app/content/posts/layout.html</link>
            <guid>https://vitepress-blog-theme.vercel.app/content/posts/layout.html</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Mar 2023 14:25:31 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[<p>当前支持的 Layout 有 <code>post</code>, <code>issue</code>, <code>doc</code>, 用来应对各种不同的场景.</p>
<div class="language-md"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">md</span><pre v-pre class="shiki material-theme-palenight" ><code><span class="line"></span></code></pre>
</div>]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>当前支持的 Layout 有 <code>post</code>, <code>issue</code>, <code>doc</code>, 用来应对各种不同的场景.</p>
<div class="language-md"><button title="Copy Code" class="copy"></button><span class="lang">md</span><pre v-pre class="shiki material-theme-palenight" ><code><span class="line"><span style="color: #A6ACCD">---</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #F07178">title</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">:</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span><span style="color: #C3E88D">Getting started</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #F07178">date</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">:</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> 2023-03-23T22:27:31+08:00</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #F07178">draft</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">:</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #FF9CAC">false</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #F07178">layout</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">:</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #C3E88D">post</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #676E95; font-style: italic"># post, issue, doc</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #F07178">tags</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">:</span><span style="color: #A6ACCD"> </span><span style="color: #89DDFF">[</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span><span style="color: #C3E88D">intro</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">&quot;</span><span style="color: #89DDFF">]</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="color: #A6ACCD">---</span></span></code></pre>
</div><h2 id="_1-post" tabindex="-1">1. post <a class="header-anchor" href="#_1-post" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;1. post&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<p>这个 layout 就是正常博客了, 不会有大纲以及侧边栏.</p>
<h2 id="_2-issue" tabindex="-1">2. issue <a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-issue" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;2. issue&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<p>通过 Github action 自动同步 issue 到博客, 可以动态的更新内容(不用在本地编辑).</p>
<h2 id="_3-doc" tabindex="-1">3. doc <a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-doc" aria-label="Permalink to &quot;3. doc&quot;">&ZeroWidthSpace;</a></h2>
<p>这个 layout 会有大纲以及侧边栏, 用来写文档, 或者做一些笔记.</p>
<p>而且它有些特殊的 <code>frontmatter</code> 字段:</p>
<ol>
<li><code>group</code> 用来分组, 会在侧边栏显示, 默认是 <code>Others</code>. 比如说我有一系列关于 <code>Rust</code> 的笔记, 你就可以设置为 <code>group = Rust 语言笔记</code></li>
</ol>
<p>示例: <a href="/MyBlog/content/docs/os/os-1.html">os1</a></p>
<hr>
<p>所有文章都必须存放在 <code>content</code> 目录下, 且 <code>layout</code> 是必须的, 但是同个 <code>layout</code> 的文章严格来讲不需要放在同个目录下.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
